&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/2212&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/2212&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-4488&quot; title=&quot;UnsupportedOperationException during initialization of StandbyTask&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-4488&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-4488&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: UnsupportedOperationException during initialization of StandbyTask&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Instead of throwing `UnsupportedOperationException` from `StandbyTask.recordCollector()` return a No-op implementation of `RecordCollector`.&lt;br/&gt;
